<p>Table 4 presents the estimated per capita death rates for each
drug. (While a number of people have died as a result of
marijuana *enforcement*, there are apparently no confirmed deaths
traceable to marijuana *use*.) The figures for cocaine and heroin
have been adjusted downward, in accordance with the previous
analysis, to include only those deaths due to drug use per se.
The unadjusted death rate for these drugs is in parentheses. </p>

