162(3859), 1234-1242.<br>
</p>

<p>Weller, R. A. (1985). Marijuana: Effects and motivation.
Medical Aspects of Human Sexuality, 19(3), 92-104.<br>
</p>

<p>Weller, R. A., Halikas, J. A., &amp; Moorse, C. (1984).
