<p><font size="1">22-Thoughts as visual images <b>0.4141</b></font>
</p>

<p><font size="1">7-Absorbed in daydream <b>0.3672</b> <b>0.4007</b></font>
</p>

<p><font size="1">32-Images easily appear <b>0.3540</b> <b>0.3855</b></font>
</p>

