<h1>The health and psychological consequences of cannabis use </h1>

<h3>National Drug Strategy<br>
Monograph Series No. 25 <br>
<br>
</h3>

<hr>

<p>Wayne Hall, Nadia Solowij and Jim Lemon, National Drug and
Alcohol Research Centre <br>
Prepared for the National Task Force on Cannabis <br>
<br>
</p>

<h3>CONTENTS </h3>

<p><a href="#acknow">Acknowledgments</a> <br>
<a href="#Exec_summ">Executive summary</a> <br>
</p>

<ul>
    <li><a href="#acute">Acute effects </a><br>
    </li>
    <li><a href="#chronic">Chronic effects</a> <br>
    </li>
    <li><a href="#high">High risk groups</a> <br>
    </li>
</ul>

<h3>The health risks of alcohol, tobacco and cannabis use </h3>

